Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.49,0:02:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是與人類同契後成為最強的武器的一種生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.79,0:02:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年酷所遇到的少女蕾也是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.87,0:02:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還是傳說中的七煌寶樹之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此蕾被各種勢力盯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.54,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是酷為了把蕾送到傳說之地——煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.95,0:02:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旅行的同伴是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼的三人組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.36,0:02:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的真正目的還是個謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.40,0:02:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏全部都是煌珠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從世界各地集中起來的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.93,0:02:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的前輩們找到並保護起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可憐的煌珠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.16,0:03:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也...我也一定會保護你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也 一定會保護你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也...我也一定會保護你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定...一定會保護你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.09,0:03:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五唱 那天的落淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路分成了兩條啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點頭緒也沒有到底哪條通往村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.07,0:04:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和奇雅走這條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.99,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶著他們兩個走那條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一天走下來沒看到村落的話就來和我們匯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們的路正確呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有幾發照明彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天黑下來就打向南面的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一看到照明彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就去你們那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是前輩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真是的 嘰哩咕嚕個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之就是我們走這條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.10,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別磨磨蹭蹭地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到個村落 找到好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.53,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡她想做的話一個人就可以保護好蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那正是我擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩對於保護蕾的方針沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是為了強行從酷身邊帶走蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而和我們走了不同的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願是我多想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方可是七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然讓達亞和摩杜去追啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人自己提出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們在擬煌珠中還算可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們嫉妒真正的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到七煌寶樹不說完好地帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打起來也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被那兩個人幹掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫蕾的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.55,0:05:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是七煌寶樹的傳言就是假的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅札蘭斯一族的最終血統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然和一個無名小卒同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.91,0:06:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人做搭擋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 這條路真的是對的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 也許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的運氣向來不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼運氣好的傢伙會失去飛船茫然不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之快點趕路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去不知什麼時候能到守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是要去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠樂園是傳說中存在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說是煌珠們誕生的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不知是否真的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.23,0:06:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾說要去的話我就一定把她送到那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為我們煌珠完全保護協會而言...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先搶錢 再要人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些粗野的人是幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶的山賊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管發生什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都會保護蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是酷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是力古嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 力古認識的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和這些粗野的人是朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 粗野...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙叫力古 以前同在一條船上當空盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是和老大他們吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的飛船墜落了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這事就別提了 力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,口氣好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.29,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來老大他們船上帶著個煌珠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說那女孩就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.17,0:08:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害的武器弄到手了口氣就大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你真是太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.86,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會打到女人的 小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小...哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰是小哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.27,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 先訂正小哥的叫法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 別擋著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是那種人 但畢竟曾是同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.10,0:09:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.18,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙什麼來頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 酷這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是個小毛孩為什麼會和煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐們 怎麼了 在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正腦袋是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有力氣就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘰哩咕嚕地在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那是核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙難道是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前的朋友做了很過分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.81,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能教我用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才也沒幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想帶蕾去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此如果沒有保護蕾的力量...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和蕾同契之後你不就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然那麼說沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.43,0:11:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害的武器弄到手了口氣就大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總在想 那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 不和你同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是她還是其他的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們守護翼的任務是保護你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不把你們只當成武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護你們不落在壞人手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以一個普普通通的人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏開開心心地度過一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是把你們作為武器使用總覺得有點怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我不和你同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑著槍和體術可以完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你永遠是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.98,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂那眼淚的含義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是因為高興而哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.68,0:13:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍是危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.25,0:13:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個要學的話就教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍微會有點痛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想著想著就睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才在想什麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 一想就困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幹什麼 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我 蕾 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是希絲卡干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我拜託她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓我不用和蕾同契也能保護蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.29,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許應該盡快把蕾帶到守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給酷的話太不可靠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.78,0:14:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.91,0:14:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊呀 好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.11,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是雷達上沒反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.15,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.14,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先給我老老實實待一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我們把那男孩解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要把酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們接受的命令有兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓住七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪走其同契者的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的性命...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.57,0:15:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和煌珠同契的人一次只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.73,0:15:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的主人就不能和那七煌寶樹同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑那個就想打敗我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開槍好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己的同契者當盾牌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們來說同契者只是用來戰鬥的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便換多少都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.97,0:16:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人類把我們當武器使用一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按原路返回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和龍威他們匯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就憑我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了 帶上蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這段時間我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想當誘餌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前的同伴被當成盾牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能救出那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就和他待在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有希絲卡在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這兒 蜘蛛大嬸們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過分 居然叫我們大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我們又不是蜘蛛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是蜘蛛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠 給我下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.35,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對酷做了不該做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我提出同契的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果盯上蕾的家夥同時也要酷的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於剛才她們說的話很在意是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和酷分開也是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷說了不想和我同契的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為不想把你當武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.13,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那樣只會使酷受傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你淚水奪眶欲出是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得酷困惑痛苦的樣子很可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...那女孩流下的眼淚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真是的 到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:17:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼想在一起的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算完成任務後將這個同契者也幹掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賣個交情兩個人一起解決好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.19,0:18:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人類當盾牌的話 就你們而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牽引之線{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.27,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此傾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與我共頌念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣息相應{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纏繞飛旋之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠相隨{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤誠之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纏繞飛揚之風{\a6}
