Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連結各自夢境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誠心誠意{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同契之後就這點水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不值一提嘛 七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強射擊有個差池的話那個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.06,0:19:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不爭取點時間的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼 這光...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.27,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在 酷 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強力無限{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連結夢境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東風之鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 願意的話和我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不打算做山賊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 我還有一定要做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從前就是說一不二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.38,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 到了村落就開始特訓哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是格鬥術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所要做的是變得和蕾更默契地戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此而做的特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.83,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.99,0:21:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天會告訴我那女孩流淚的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.64,0:22:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被雨淋濕的墓碑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.10,0:22:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是呆呆地凝視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.60,0:22:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰冷的土地之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.80,0:22:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連悲傷也埋葬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.15,0:23:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 凝視同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.73,0:23:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六唱 凝視同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時她還是個少女

